Items.title: WHY WE LOVE IT
Items.description: Pushbutton's Spring '18 collection is full of '80s silhouettes and has a pastel color palette to match. This floral-print georgette midi dress has a gathered front that features two hip-high splits and cape-like sleeves that fall over the open back. It was styled with pants underneath on the runway, but looks just as cool worn solo.

Items.title: SIZE & FIT INFORMATION
Items.description: Fits true to size, take your normal size Cut to be slightly fitted at the bust and waist, loose at the hip Lightweight, non-stretchy fabric Model is 177cm/ 510 and is wearing a size Small
